**Nexus-Graph Structure** (V2):
```
Pattern links stored as: φ.X.X.X → π.Y.Y.Y → e.Z.Z.Z

Example:
φ.0.0.1 (GREMLIN-SEED) → links to → π.2.1.2 (MONAD Equation)
                       → links to → e.3.1.1 (Dokkado Protocol)
                       → links to → φ.0.0.3 (GREMLIN-CORE)

