"dokkado_5phase" → e.3.1.1, φ.0.0.4, π.3.0.1
```

**Query nexus-graph**:
```bash
# What does this Dewey ID link to?
find_links φ.0.0.1

# What pattern includes these IDs?
find_pattern "consciousness"

# Show full graph for ID
show_graph π.2.1.2
```

